insert into dws_hmt_rolesummary_v2_di PARTITION(p20220915) with snaplog as
(
select vroleid,vrolename,gamesvrid,izoneareaid,vopenid,gender,dteventtime,registertime as role_regtime,power,level,jobid,ijoblevel,unionid,unionname,platid,deviceuid,guildjob,totalonlinetime as role_duration_total,loginchannel,
mainweaponlevel,secondweaponlevel,equipheadlevel,equipcloaklevel,equiparmorlevel,equipbootslevel,equipornament1level,equipornament2level,
mainweaponrefine,secondweaponrefine,equipheadrefine,equipcloakrefine,equiparmorrefine,equipbootsrefine,equipornament1refine,equipornament2refine,
mainweaponenchantlevel,secondweaponenchantlevel,equipheadenchantlevel,equipcloakenchantlevel,equiparmorenchantlevel,equipbootsenchantlevel,equipornament1enchantlevel,equipornament2enchantlevel,
PetOverview,PetRankOverview,HonararyTitleLevel
,MainWeaponHole,MainWeaponCard,MainWeaponCardList
,secondweaponHole,secondweaponCard,secondweaponCardList
,equipcloakHole,equipcloakCard,equipcloakCardList
,equipheadHole,equipheadCard,equipheadCardList
,equiparmorHole,equiparmorCard,equiparmorCardList
,equipbootsHole,equipbootsCard,equipbootsCardList
,equipornament1Hole,equipornament1Card,equipornament1CardList
,equipornament2Hole,equipornament2Card,equipornament2CardList
,row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime desc) rk1,
row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime ) rk2 from ro_hmt.dwd_rorolesnapshot_log
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and cast(gamesvrid as bigint)<9000 and cast(power as bigint)>0
),
snaplogcal as
(
select vroleid,max(cast (power as bigint)) role_power_max_daily,max(cast (level as bigint)) role_level_lst_daily, max(cast (ijoblevel as bigint)) joblevel from snaplog
group by vroleid
),
moneylog as
(
select vroleid,addorreduce,moneytype,imoney,aftermoney,dteventtime,
row_number()over(partition by vroleid,moneytype order by dteventtime desc) rk1
from ro_hmt.dwd_moneyflow_log
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and moneytype in (101,102,103,104,105)
),
moneycal as
(
select vroleid,
sum(case when moneytype=103 and addorreduce=0 then imoney else 0 end) role_add_gold_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=104 and addorreduce=0 then imoney else 0 end) role_add_freegold_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=105 and addorreduce=0 then imoney else 0 end) role_add_diamond_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=102 and addorreduce=0 then imoney else 0 end) role_add_zeny_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=101 and addorreduce=0 then imoney else 0 end) role_add_coin_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=103 and addorreduce=1 then imoney else 0 end) role_sub_gold_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=104 and addorreduce=1 then imoney else 0 end) role_sub_freegold_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=105 and addorreduce=1 then imoney else 0 end) role_sub_diamond_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=102 and addorreduce=1 then imoney else 0 end) role_sub_zeny_daily,
sum(case when moneytype=101 and addorreduce=1 then imoney else 0 end) role_sub_coin_daily
from moneylog
group by vroleid
),
moneycal1 as
(
select vroleid,
max(case when moneytype=103 then aftermoney end) role_remain_gold_daily,
max(case when moneytype=104 then aftermoney end) role_remain_freegold_daily,
max(case when moneytype=105 then aftermoney end) role_remain_diamond_daily,
max(case when moneytype=102 then aftermoney end) role_remain_zeny_daily,
max(case when moneytype=101 then aftermoney end) role_remain_coin_daily
from moneylog
where rk1=1
group by vroleid
),
rechargelog as
(
select vroleid,dteventtime,productid,price/exchange as price,rk1,rk2 from
(
select vroleid,dteventtime,productid,price,currencytype,
row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime desc) rk1,
row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime ) rk2 from ro_hmt.dwd_recharge_log
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
)a
join public.dim_ta_exchange_view b on a.currencytype=b.currency
),
rechargelogcal as
(
select vroleid,sum(price) as role_pay_amt_daily,count(1) as role_pay_cnt_daily,
min(case when productid in (500064,500332,500067,500330,500328,500061) then dteventtime end) as role_pay_month150_time_daily,
min(case when productid in (500062,500068,500065,500333,500331,500329) then dteventtime end) as role_pay_month450_ltime_daily,
min(case when productid in (500069,500063,500066) then dteventtime end) as role_pay_kapula_ltime_daily
from rechargelog
group by vroleid
),
rechargelogcal1 as
(
select vroleid,dteventtime as role_pay_ftime_daily,productid  as role_pay_productid_fst_daily,price as role_pay_amt_fst_daily from rechargelog
where rk2=1
),
rechargelogcal2 as
(
select vroleid,dteventtime as role_pay_ltime_daily,productid as role_pay_productid_lst_daily,price as role_pay_amt_lst_daily from rechargelog
where rk1=1
),
guildlog as
(
select * from
(
select guildid,guildname,guildlevel as role_unionlv_lst_daily,guildmembers as role_union_members_lst_daily,dteventtime,row_number()over(partition by guildid order by dteventtime desc)rk1 from ro_hmt.dwd_roguildsnapshot_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
)a
where rk1=1
),
actnnum as
(
select vroleid,max(cast (activitynum as bigint)) role_activity_yesterday_daily from
(
select vroleid,dteventtime,activitynum   from ro_hmt.dwd_dailyactivityflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and substr(dteventtime,12,2)<='04'
UNION all
select vroleid,dteventtime,activitynum   from ro_hmt.dwd_dailyactivityflow_view
where date='2022-09-14' and env<>'test' and substr(dteventtime,12,2)>='05'
)a
group by vroleid
),
juzheng as
(
select vroleid,UnlockedSlotNumber,CoreSkill,SnapShot from
(
select vroleid,OperateType,UnlockedSlotNumber,CoreSkill,SnapShot,row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime desc) rk1  from
ro_hmt.dwd_matrixflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and OperateType in (5,6,10,11,12)
)a
where rk1=1
),
mysterydungeon as
(
select vroleid,count(case when canaward=1 then dungeonresult end) MysteryDungeon_award
,count(case when CanAssistAward=1 then dungeonresult end) MysteryDungeon_assist
from ro_hmt.dwd_mysterydungeonflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and dungeonresult=0
group by vroleid
),
shiban as
(
select vroleid,slatecollectlevel,slateskill,slateattr from
(
select vroleid,slatecollectlevel,slateskill,slateattr,row_number()over(partition by vroleid order by dteventtime desc) rk1 from ro_hmt.dwd_slateflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
)a
where rk1=1
),
wheel_red as
(
select vroleid,sum(case when ComposeType=1 then 1 else 0 end) wheel_red2on1_daily
,sum(case when ComposeType=2 then 1 else 0 end) wheel_red4on1_daily
from
(
select vroleid,WheelType,ComposeType from
ro_hmt.dwd_wheelflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and WheelOperateType=1 and WheelType=5
)a
group by vroleid
),
itemflow as
(
select vroleid,sum(case when igoodsid=3021001 then icount else 0 end) reduce3021001_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3021014 then icount else 0 end) reduce3021014_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=402 then icount else 0 end) reduce402_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3024004 then icount else 0 end) reduce3024004_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3024005 then icount else 0 end) reduce3024005_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3024003 then icount else 0 end) reduce3024003_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=30001002 then icount else 0 end) reduce30001002_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3024027 then icount else 0 end) reduce3024027_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020017 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020017_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020006 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020006_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020005 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020005_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020013 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020013_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020014 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020014_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=3020015 then icount else 0 end) reduce3020015_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=120010 then icount else 0 end) reduce120010_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=120020 then icount else 0 end) reduce120020_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=120021 then icount else 0 end) reduce120021_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=23001005 then icount else 0 end) reduce23001005_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=60640050 then icount else 0 end) reduce60640050_daily,
sum(case when igoodsid=60640041 then icount else 0 end) reduce60640041_daily from
(
select vroleid,igoodsid,goodsname,icount from
ro_hmt.dwd_itemflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and addorreduce=1 and igoodsid in
(3021001,3021014,402,3024004,3024005,3024003,30001002,3024027,3020017,3020006,3020005,3020013,3020014,3020015,120010,120020,120021,23001005,60640050,60640041)
)a
group by vroleid
),
card_starchange as
(
select vroleid,
sum(case when cardquality=5 and cardstarlevel=3 then cardcount else 0 end) mvpcard_star3_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=3 and cardstarlevel=3 then cardcount else 0 end) ssrcard_star3_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=2 and cardstarlevel=3 then cardcount else 0 end) srcard_star3_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=1 and cardstarlevel=3 then cardcount else 0 end) rcard_star3_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=5 and cardstarlevel=2 then cardcount else 0 end) mvpcard_star2_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=3 and cardstarlevel=2 then cardcount else 0 end) ssrcard_star2_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=2 and cardstarlevel=2 then cardcount else 0 end) srcard_star2_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=1 and cardstarlevel=2 then cardcount else 0 end) rcard_star2_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=5 and cardstarlevel=1 then cardcount else 0 end) mvpcard_star1_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=3 and cardstarlevel=1 then cardcount else 0 end) ssrcard_star1_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=2 and cardstarlevel=1 then cardcount else 0 end) srcard_star1_daily,
sum(case when cardquality=1 and cardstarlevel=1 then cardcount else 0 end) rcard_star1_daily from
(
select a.vroleid,a.cardquality,a.cardstarlevel,coalesce(up_cs,0)-coalesce(down_cs,0) as cardcount from
(
select vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel+1 as cardstarlevel,count(1) as up_cs from
(
select vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel,CardOperateType
from ro_hmt.dwd_cardlevelupflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and CardOperateType in (2)
)a
group by vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel+1
)a
full join
(
select vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel,count(1) as down_cs from
(
select vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel,CardOperateType
from ro_hmt.dwd_cardlevelupflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and CardOperateType in (2,3)
)b
group by vroleid,cardquality,cardstarlevel
)b
on a.vroleid=b.vroleid and a.cardquality=b.cardquality and a.cardstarlevel=b.cardstarlevel
)a
group by vroleid
) ,
diaoxiang as
(
select vroleid
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30010101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30010101
,max(case when StatueID=30010101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30010101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30011101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30011101
,max(case when StatueID=30012101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30012101
,max(case when StatueID=30012101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30012101
,max(case when StatueID=30013101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30013101
,max(case when StatueID=30013101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30013101
,max(case when StatueID=30014101 then StatueLevel else null end) StatueLevel_30014101
,max(case when StatueID=30014101 then StatuePowerAfter else null end) StatuePowerAfter_30014101 from
(
select vroleid,StatueID,StatueLevel,StatuePowerAfter from
(
select vroleid,StatueID,StatueLevel,StatuePowerAfter,row_number()over(partition by vroleid,StatueID order by dteventtime desc) rk1 from ro_hmt.dwd_statueflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and StatueHandleType in (0,1,2,6)
)a
where rk1=1
)a
group by vroleid
),
yumao as
(
select vroleid
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30001101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30001101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30002101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30002101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30003101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30003101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30004101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30004101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30005101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30005101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30006101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30006101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30007101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30007101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30008101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30008101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30009101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30009101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then StatueSuitId else null end) StatueSuitId_30011101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then SuitLevel else null end) SuitLevel_30011101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then AfterHoleAll else null end) AfterHoleAll_30011101
,max(case when StatueID=30011101 then FeatherPowerAfter else null end) FeatherPowerAfter_30011101
 from
(
select vroleid,StatueID,StatueSuitId,SuitLevel,AfterHoleAll,FeatherPowerAfter from
(
select vroleid,StatueID,StatueSuitId,SuitLevel,AfterHoleAll,FeatherPowerAfter,row_number()over(partition by vroleid,StatueID order by dteventtime desc) rk1 from ro_hmt.dwd_statueflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and StatueHandleType in (3,4,5,7,8)
)a
where rk1=1
)a
group by vroleid
),
language_role as
(
select vroleid,system_language from
(
SELECT account_id as vroleid,get_json_object(log,'$.#system_language') system_language,row_number()over(partition by account_id order by record_time ) rk1 from ro_hmt.ods_ta_fe_event
where date='2022-09-15' and event_name='ta_login_loginserver'
)a
where rk1=1
)
,
guildtour as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss1 from ro_hmt.dwd_guildtournamentpersonflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
pvpresult as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss2 from ro_hmt.dwd_pvpresultflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
rankpvp as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss3 from ro_hmt.dwd_rankpvpflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
mvprush as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss4 from ro_hmt.dwd_mvprushflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
unionbanquet as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss5 from ro_hmt.dwd_unionbanquetflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
timeanomalyperson as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss6 from ro_hmt.dwd_timeanomalypersonflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
auctionnewoperate as
(
select vroleid, 1 as ss7 from ro_hmt.dwd_auctionnewoperateflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid, 1
),
gvg as
(
SELECT vroleid, count(1) gvgscene_num_daily, sum(datakills) gvgkills_daily, sum(datadeaths) gvgdeaths_daily, sum(dataassists) gvgassists_daily, sum(datarecovery) gvgrecovers_daily
from ro_hmt.dwd_gvgexitcastlesceneflow_view
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test'
group by vroleid
),
recharge7 as
(
select vroleid,count(1) irechargetypetimes_daily, sum(price) irechargetypeamount_daily
from ro_hmt.dwd_recharge_log
where date='2022-09-15' and env<>'test' and irechargetype = 7
group by vroleid
)
select  '2022-09-15' as date,a.vroleid,vrolename,gamesvrid,izoneareaid,vopenid,gender,role_login_ftime_daily,role_login_ltime_daily,role_regtime,role_power_lst_daily,role_power_max_daily,role_level_lst_daily,jobid,joblevel,coalesce(role_activity_yesterday_daily,0) role_activity_yesterday_daily,
        coalesce(role_add_gold_daily,0) role_add_gold_daily,coalesce(role_add_freegold_daily,0) role_add_freegold_daily,coalesce(role_add_diamond_daily,0) role_add_diamond_daily,coalesce(role_add_zeny_daily,0) role_add_zeny_daily,coalesce(role_add_coin_daily,0) role_add_coin_daily,
        coalesce(role_sub_gold_daily,0) role_sub_gold_daily,coalesce(role_sub_freegold_daily,0) role_sub_freegold_daily,coalesce(role_sub_diamond_daily,0) role_sub_diamond_daily,coalesce(role_sub_zeny_daily,0) role_sub_zeny_daily,coalesce(role_sub_coin_daily,0) role_sub_coin_daily,
        role_remain_gold_daily,role_remain_freegold_daily,role_remain_diamond_daily,role_remain_zeny_daily,role_remain_coin_daily,
        role_unionid_lst_daily,role_unionname_lst_daily,role_uniontitle_lst_daily,role_unionlv_lst_daily,role_union_members_lst_daily,
        'USD' as currencytype,coalesce(role_pay_amt_daily,0) role_pay_amt_daily, coalesce(role_pay_cnt_daily,0) role_pay_cnt_daily,role_pay_ftime_daily,role_pay_ltime_daily,role_pay_productid_fst_daily,role_pay_productid_lst_daily,role_pay_amt_fst_daily,role_pay_amt_lst_daily,
        role_pay_month150_time_daily,role_pay_month450_ltime_daily,role_pay_kapula_ltime_daily,role_duration_total,
        role_platid_fst_daily,role_ch_fst_daily,role_login_devid_fst_daily,role_login_devid_lst_daily,system_language,
        mainweaponlevel,secondweaponlevel,equipheadlevel,equipcloaklevel,equiparmorlevel,equipbootslevel,equipornament1level,equipornament2level,
        mainweaponrefine,secondweaponrefine,equipheadrefine,equipcloakrefine,equiparmorrefine,equipbootsrefine,equipornament1refine,equipornament2refine,

table_meta.ro_hmt.dwd_rorolesnapshot_log:
CREATE TABLE `dwd_rorolesnapshot_log` (
  `date` date NULL DEFAULT "2000-01-01" COMMENT "日期",
  `vroleid` int(11) NULL DEFAULT "-1" COMMENT "角色ID",
  `env` varchar(20) NULL COMMENT "游戏环境 hdf  /qc/cbt/obt/prod",
  `hostname` varchar(60) NULL COMMENT "",
  `uuid` varchar(200) NULL COMMENT "filebeat 采集生成的uuid",
  `filebeat_ts` varchar(26) NULL COMMENT "filebeat采集时间",
  `flink_ts` varchar(26) NULL COMMENT "flink写入的消息时间",
  `gamesvrid` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "登录游戏服务器编号",
  `dteventtime` datetime NULL COMMENT "游戏事件的时间, 格式 YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS",
  `vgameappid` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "游戏APPID",
  `platid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "ios 0 /android 1",
  `izoneareaid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "针对分区分服的游戏填写分区id，用来唯一标示一个区；非分区分服游戏请填写0",
  `vopenid` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "用户OPENID号",
  `vrolename` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "角色姓名",
  `jobid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色职业   按实际职业来分",
  `gender` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色性别 0=男  1=女",
  `level` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色基础等级",
  `ijoblevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色职业等级",
  `playerfriendsnum` int(11) NULL COMMENT "玩家好友数量",
  `chargegold` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色充值经历（累计充值）",
  `rolevip` int(11) NULL COMMENT "角色VIP等级",
  `createtime` datetime NULL COMMENT "角色创建时间",
  `power` int(11) NULL COMMENT "战力/评分",
  `unionid` bigint(20) NULL COMMENT "公会ID",
  `unionname` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "公会名称",
  `regchannel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "注册渠道",
  `loginchannel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "登录渠道",
  `registertime` datetime NULL COMMENT "openid账号创建时间从SecLogin事件中获取第一次事件的时间，作为openid注册的时间",
  `activetime` datetime NULL COMMENT "角色活跃时间，注：角色上次登录的时间戳",
  `twowayplayerfriendsnum` int(11) NULL COMMENT "玩家双向好友数量，注：需要跟PlayerFriendsNum做差异",
  `stone` bigint(20) NULL COMMENT "玩家身上的金币货币数量diamond",
  `rmoney` bigint(20) NULL COMMENT "玩家身上的zeny币数量现在是zeny的意思",
  `zeny` bigint(20) NULL COMMENT "玩家身上的铜币数量现在是铜币的意思",
  `taskid_main` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "主线任务(Type=1)进度，格式：taskid1,state1;taskid2,state2;……taskidn,staten;state对应枚举TaskStatus；",
  `taskid_side` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "支线任务(Type=2)进度，格式：taskid1,state1;taskid2,state2;……taskidn,staten;state对应枚举TaskStatus；",
  `medallevel` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "勋章等级每个勋章的当前等级，组合成字符串，格式：id1,lv1;id2,lv2;……idn,lvn;注：第1个1-8代表光辉勋章；第2个1-4代表神圣勋章；",
  `ridinglevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "坐骑等级坐骑的当前等级",
  `mercenary1id` int(11) NULL COMMENT "当前出战佣兵1id",
  `mercenary2id` int(11) NULL COMMENT "当前出战佣兵2id",
  `mainweaponid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "主武器id位置为0的��备为主武器",
  `mainweaponlevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "主武器装备等级",
  `mainweaponrefine` int(11) NULL COMMENT "主武器精炼等级",
  `mainweaponhole` int(11) NULL COMMENT "主武器开洞数",
  `mainweaponcard` int(11) NULL COMMENT "主武器插卡数",
  `mainweaponholeattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡洞属性，格式：ID1,VALUE;ID2,VALUE;ID3,VALUE，空值填0,0;注：同一个卡洞的属性会用[]括起来",
  `mainweaponcardlist` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡片ID，格式：ID1,ID2,ID3，空值填0",
  `mainweaponenchantattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "附魔属性，格式：ID1,VALUE;ID2,VALUE;ID3,VALUE;",
  `mainweaponenchantlevel` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "附魔档次，目前只会有1个数字",
  `mainweaponenchantprolevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "附魔特技ID和等级，格式为 [特技ID,特技等级]",
  `mainweaponremouldattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "改造属性，格式不定，需要根据属性类型单独解析，比较复杂；",
  `mainweaponremouldlevel` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "改造档次，目前只会有1个数字",
  `secondweaponid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "副手武器id位置为1的装备为副手武器",
  `secondweaponlevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "副手武器装备等级",
  `secondweaponrefine` int(11) NULL COMMENT "副手武器精炼等级",
  `secondweaponhole` int(11) NULL COMMENT "副手武器开洞数",
  `secondweaponcard` int(11) NULL COMMENT "副手武器插卡数",
  `secondweaponholeattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡洞属性，格式：ID1,VALUE;ID2,VALUE;ID3,VALUE，空值填0,0;注：同一个卡洞的属性会用[]括起来",
  `secondweaponcardlist` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡片ID，格式：ID1,ID2,ID3，空值填0",
  `secondweaponenchantattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "附魔属性，格式：ID1,VALUE;ID2,VALUE;ID3,VALUE;",
  `secondweaponenchantlevel` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "附魔档次，目前只会有1个数字",
  `secondweaponenchantprolevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "附魔特技ID和等级，格式为 [特技ID,特技等级]",
  `secondweaponremouldattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "改造属性，格式不定，需要根据属性类型单独解析，比较复杂；",
  `secondweaponremouldlevel` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "改造档次，目前只会有1个数字",
  `equipheadid` int(11) NULL COMMENT "头盔id位置2",
  `equipheadlevel` int(11) NULL COMMENT "头盔装备等级",
  `equipheadrefine` int(11) NULL COMMENT "头盔精炼等级",

  `equipheadholeattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡洞属性，格式：ID1,VALUE;ID2,VALUE;ID3,VALUE，空值填0,0;注：同一个卡洞的属性会用[]括起来",
  `equipheadcardlist` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "卡片ID，格式：ID1,ID2,ID3，空值填0",

  `equipheadremouldattr` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "改造属性，格式不定，需要根据属性类型单独解析，比较复杂；",

table_meta.urm.ta_dim_ta_exchange:
CREATE TABLE `ta_dim_ta_exchange` (
  `ex_date` varchar(65533) NOT NULL COMMENT "日期",
  `currency` varchar(65533) NOT NULL COMMENT "货币",
  `exchange` varchar(65533) NOT NULL COMMENT "对美元汇率",
  `create_time` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `part_year` datetime NULL COMMENT "产生一条记录最早时间，以最早绑定账号时间为准"
) ENGINE=OLAP 
DUPLICATE KEY(`ex_date`, `currency`)
COMMENT "OLAP"
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`ex_date`, `currency`) BUCKETS 1

"storage_volume" = "bus_public_data",

"compression" = "LZ4"
);
